  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The peaceful Dolpik Isles are under attack by the notorious Gooble gang. They have stolen the power of the sun metals and the only one that can stop them is Anna, a cheerful inventor who just had her and her brother's vacation ruined!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this 3D platformer collectathon it's up to you to save the Dolpik Isles and save your vacation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>In this collectathon there are:</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-6 levels to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-7 boss to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-60 Sun metals to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-70 blue coins scattered in the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Character customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Mini games.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The peaceful Dolpik Isles are under attack by the notorious Gooble gang. They have stolen the power of the sun metals and the only one that can stop them is Anna, a cheerful inventor who just had her and her brother's vacation ruined!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this 3D platformer collectathon it's up to you to save the Dolpik Isles and save your vacation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>In this collectathon there are:</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-6 levels to explore.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-7 boss to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-60 Sun metals to find.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-70 blue coins scattered in the levels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Fishing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Character customization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-Mini games.</p>",
